<br>
Easiest way to take him out:<br>
<br>
1. Mem your 49 or 51 earth pet.  DS/BO3 him.<br>
2. Pull Dino to the shore.  Send in your pet.  Run to other side of the island.<br>
3. When your pet dies, start casting the new one.  BO3/DS him.  By the time you finish, Dino will be almost on top of you, so send him in, and run to the other side of the island.<br>
4. Rinse and repeat.  Takes 5-6 49th level pets usually, 4-5 51st level pets.<br>
<br>
Trickier, but faster method of killing him:<br>
<br>
1. Mem 54 water and 51 earth.  Load up your lava bolt.  Make sure you have sow or run3 or a horse.  Levitate is good, too.<br>
2. Cast 54 water, BO3/DS/Expedience him.  Don't let him taunt.<br>
3. Face *away* from Dino, start casting your bolt.  The instant it finishes, start casting again.  Your first bolt will hit about the same time that your second one finishes casting.  Send in your pet, and run like hell.<br>
4. Keep an eye on Dino... when he stops to attack your pet, blast him again with lava bolts to regain agro.<br>
<br>
If you do this right, you'll keep agro and your pet will be backstabbing his way along.  It's taken me a few tries, but I can usually kill Dino without losing my water pet, and only using about 3 bubs of mana at 54.<br>
<br>
If your water pet dies, you have a choice: try to recast a water pet, or switch to chaincasting earth.  Personally, I go for chaincasting earth.  It's not fun when Dino catches up to you :-) <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showMessageRange?topicID=107.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showMessageRange?topicID=107.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showPrevMessage?topicID=107.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showNextMessage?topicID=107.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=107.topic&index=44><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.threadControl?topicID=107.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=107.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=107.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=